            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>and <strong>chopped creamed</strong> <strong>coconut </strong>in 300ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>with the <strong>smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>ground cumin </strong>and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> – this is your <strong>spiced stock</strong></p>",
