    {
      "instruction": "<p>Rinse the<strong> white long grain rice</strong> until the water runs clear</p><p>Add<strong> </strong>the<strong> rinsed rice </strong>to<strong> </strong>an <strong>oven-proof dish </strong>with the <strong>spiced stock </strong>and a very generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>sliced shallot</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>chopped beans </strong>and <strong>chopped mango </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p>",
